casebody.data:
F. L. REVELL v. J. G. ANDERSON REALTY COMPANY 16 So. (2nd) 640

January Term, 1944

February 11, 1944 En Banc I. P. Barlow and W. W. Whitehurst, for appellant. L. Grady Burton, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

No reversible error is made to appear and, therefore, judgment is affirmed.

So ordered.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, BROWN, ADAMS and SE-BRING, JJ., concur. THOMAS, J., dissents. CHAPMAN, J., not participating.
